page_title: Azure OpenAI Service encryption of data at rest
page_description: Learn how Azure OpenAI encrypts your data when it's persisted to the cloud.
chunk_content: Update the key versionWhen you create a new version of a key, update the Azure AI services resource to use the new version. Follow these steps:1. Go to your Azure AI services resource, and then select Encryption.1. Enter the URI for the new key version. Alternately, you can select the key vault and then select the key again to update the version.1. Save your changes.
